{"title":"老枣树下","authors":["牛雅杰"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老枣树下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛雅杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老枣树下吃甜枣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着枣子热泪冒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜中思苦眼睛亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事呵！多少、多少……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十年前爷爷栽下这棵枣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树刚刚长高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷呵，因为交不起租子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这棵树上吊死了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲长大，决心把仇报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东奔西跑，找了一把大刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知刀还没有磨好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲就被地主抓走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪名——“强盗”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲被绑在枣树上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮开肉烂滚水浇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈坐在树下痛哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠心的地主呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着她心窝猛扎一刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹妈被杀害了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家产被霸占了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我砍下一根枣刺条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四处流落、乞讨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老枣树呵高高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血海深仇记得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老枣树呵，你记下咱穷人的仇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱穷人翻身你也看见了。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}